					<h2>F.A.Q.</h2>
				</div>
				
				<div class="ngt-faq-question">When can I download the movie?</div>
				<div class="ngt-faq-answer">There are some expensive legal fees that come with distributing your film online. I&rsquo;m an independent filmmaker and I work full&ndash;time, so I&rsquo;m saving up money and inching towards being able to do that. I anticipate downloads will be available by the end of the year, but until then we are focusing on screening the film in theaters throughout 2015.</div>
				
				<div class="ngt-faq-question">Can I set up a screening in my town?</div>
				<div class="ngt-faq-answer">Totally! We have set up screenings in Berlin, Arizona, Florida, Texas and Los Angeles. If you book stuff in your town and want to set something up, e-mail me.</div>
				
				<div class="ngt-faq-question">Where is my backer reward?</div>
				<div class="ngt-faq-answer">We sent out all the backer rewards at the end of 2014, and we sent several messages to the backers asking for correct addresses/sizes etc. If you didn&rsquo;t get your reward, I apologize, but we tried our best to get a response from you and the odds are you either moved or didn&rsquo;t answer the survey. Digital downloads will go out by the end of the year.</div>
				
				<div class="ngt-faq-question">Do you have extra rewards from the Kickstarter?</div>
				<div class="ngt-faq-answer">We do still have some of Mitch Clem&rsquo;s posters. If you are interested in buying one e&ndash;mail me. There are no more stickers or t-shirts.</div>
			</div>
